<h3 id="motions-in-the-plane">Motions in the plane</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>However, there is some systematic behavior, and the simplest is the following: At any time instant t0, the normals to the trajectories pass through a point p(t0) (or they are parallel).</p>
</blockquote>

