<h3 id="sweeping-and-skinning">Sweeping and Skinning</h3>

<p><img src="/images/posts/AG/12-30 motion sweeping.png" height="510" width="660" /></p>
<blockquote>
  <p>Whereas sweeping often does not allow us to precisely prescribe the location of the sources in space, there is a method for doing so. It is called <strong>skinning</strong>, which wraps a surface (skin) over a given network of curves.</p>
